a few months ago i was detected with a skin disease called psoriasis, the truth is that this has affected my life, it has given me depression, i cry non-stop and  i have been desperate, with a lot of stress because i don’t understand how this could have developed in me. right now i am undergoing treatment and i hope to improve. i am putting on my best attitude and people around who have made this not so hard for me (so thankful 4 that) i try not to show it but sometimes my mind goes crazyyy and I would like to have my hands and feet as before but my reality is different, but here we are and the important thing is only that “life to live” ❤️‍🩹🙏

 #psoriasis #psoroasiswarrior #skindisease
i know i can’t afford to stop for one moment
